Interaction Notes:
- Links: Click → smooth scroll to section (#work, #about)
- Social: Click → new tab (rel="noopener noreferrer")
- CV: Click → download PDF
- Menu: Click → open menu modal/drawer (future enhancement)
- Hover: Links show opacity: 1.0 transition (200ms)

Accessibility:
- Role: navigation
- Skip to content: Hidden link before nav (visible on focus)
- ARIA labels: Menu button needs aria-label="Open menu"
- Focus visible: 2px outline on all links

Responsive:
- Fixed/sticky at top of viewport (z-index: var(--z-index-sticky))
- Background: backdrop-blur + bg-white/60 when scrolled >50px
